snippet.textDisplay: For information of all Pakistanis, this is the language spoken by majority of people in maqbouza Kashmir(particularly by ethnic  Kashmiris), it's know  as Koshur(kashmiri) language.Koshur( Kashmiri)is a dardic language like Shina, khowari,kafiri nooristani and is only dardic language with considerable amount of literature The important dialects spoken are Kishtwari, Poguli, and Rambani.
